public abstract class AbstractPersistenceOperation<P extends PersistentObject<?>>
extends AbstractPoOperation<P>

Abstract persistence operation. This operation affects a PersistentObject that is Accessible via the getPo() method. A persistence worker is automatically created by the default factory.
